comment:
* A listener for asynchronous geocoding results. Only one of the methods will ever be invoked
     * per geocoding attempt. There are no guarantees on how long it will take for a method to be
     * invoked, nor any guarantees on the format or availability of error information.

methods.name: void onGeocode(@NonNull List<Address> addresses)
methods.comment: Invoked when geocoding completes successfully. May return an empty list.

methods.name: void onError(@Nullable String errorMessage)
methods.comment: Invoked when geocoding fails, with an optional error message.
